      "description": "Particle image velocimetry (PIV) flow fields and normalized index of hemolysis (NIH) measurements collected at the FDA laboratory for the generic centrifugal blood pump across 5 flow-speed operating points. This dataset was finalized and archived on 2025-09-04, three weeks before the model revision on 2025-09-25 that updated tip-clearance geometry and viscosity sub-model coefficients. The assessment team asserts the revision was 'not material' to the experimental boundary conditions captured in this dataset; however, no formal re-validation run against the revised model build (v3r2) was performed using this dataset prior to submission.",
